to remove the top line,

~/.mozilla/firefox/profile/chrome/userChrome.css

modification is needed.

First of all, go to about:config, and change the value of toolkit.legacyUserProfileCustomizations.stylesheets to true.

#profile can be found in Firefox, help > Troubleshooting Information

the file is copied as \chrome\userChrome.css
if chomre directory is not found, make one.
